# Portfolio Website Walkthrough - Tanishka Khandelwal

## Overview

I have successfully built a **modern, responsive, premium portfolio website** for Tanishka Khandelwal based on the provided specifications. The website features a Gen-Z aesthetic with glassmorphism, neumorphic cards, smooth animations, and a blue-purple-teal color palette.

