- **Body**: Inter (300-500 weight)

### Components
- **Glass Panel**: Backdrop blur + semi-transparent background
- **Neumorphic Card**: Soft shadows, rounded corners (24px), hover effects
- **Buttons**: Rounded full, gradient primary, glassmorphic secondary
- **Animations**: Fade-in, slide-up, scale, floating effects

